column4: "Property `userGroup` should be a valid IRI to an existing UserGroup."
"Property `name` has a min length of 2 characters."
"Property `name` has a max length of 255 characters."
"Property `model` should be a valid IRI to an existing Device Model."
"Property `site` should be a valid IRI to an existing Site."
"Property `network` should be a valid IRI to an existing Network."
"Property `platform` should be a valid IRI to an existing Platform."
"Property `serialNumber` has a min length of 2 characters."
"Property `serialNumber` has a max length of 255 characters."
"Property `macAddress` has a min length of 2 characters."
"Property `macAddress` has a max length of 17 characters."
"Property `osVersion` has a min length of 1 characters."
"Property `osVersion` has a max length of 10 characters."
"Property `wantedOsVersion` has a min length of 1 characters."
"Property `wantedOsVersion` has a max length of 10 characters."
"Property `softwareVersion` has a min length of 1 characters."
"Property `softwareVersion` has a max length of 10 characters."
"Property `wantedSoftwareVersion` has a min length of 1 characters."
"Property `wantedSoftwareVersion` has a max length of 10 characters."
"Property `diagnostic` should be a valid IRI to an existing Device Diagnostic."
"Property `status` should be a valid IRI to an existing Device Status."
"Property `outputs` should be a an array of valid IRIs to existing Device Output."
